OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'devoted' head
OL,4,Cteacher killed in collision
OL,6,FA "beloved" head teacher who died in
OL,7,Fan alleged hit-and-run has been
OL,8,Fdescribed as a "devoted" father who
OL,9,Fgave his family "fantastic memories".
OL,11,FMichael Mullins died on Monday 20
OL,12,FApril 2026 following a collision
OL,13,Fbetween his bicycle and a car on
OL,14,FPaddock Lane in Altrincham, Greater
OL,15,FManchester, just after 6pm.
OL,17,FThe 56-year-old was the long-serving
OL,18,Fheadteacher of Stretford Grammar
OL,19,FSchool, which was closed to students
OL,20,Fon Tuesday 21 April following his
OL,21,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
