OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776848753
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'devoted' head
OL,4,Cteacher killed in collision
OL,6,FMichael's family have paid tribute to
OL,7,Ftheir "loving Dad".
OL,9,FThey said: "Our loving Dad, husband,
OL,10,FBrother-in-law, 'Diddy', Uncle, Son in
OL,11,Flaw, passed away last night after
OL,12,Fbeing knocked off his bike.
OL,14,F"He was devoted to his family, and our
OL,15,Flives will never be the same. A gap
OL,16,Fhas been left in our hearts and within
OL,17,Fhis role as a headteacher of Stretford
OL,18,FGrammar school.
OL,26,@oD@GOUqD@LOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776848753
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'devoted' head
OL,4,Cteacher killed in collision
OL,6,F"Our Dad gave us fantastic memories
OL,7,Fgrowing up including a trip getting
OL,8,Flost at night around Washington D.C
OL,9,Fbut it was in his role as a Grandad
OL,10,Fwhere he truly excelled.
OL,12,F"Our love and memories of Michael will
OL,13,Fknow no limits.
OL,15,F"We will love him forever, to Saturn
OL,16,Fand beyond."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
