CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776848753
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'devoted' head
OL,4,Cteacher killed in collision
OL,6,FThree men and one woman have been
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of causing death
OL,8,Fby dangerous driving after the car
OL,9,Finvolved in the collision failed to
OL,10,Fstop.
OL,12,FPaying tribute, Stretford and Urmston
OL,13,FMP Andrew Western said: "I am shocked
OL,14,Fand truly saddened to hear the
OL,15,Fdevastating news of Mr Mullins' tragic
OL,16,Fdeath. My thoughts and condolences go
OL,17,Fout to the staff and students at
OL,18,FStretford Grammar, and above all to
OL,19,FMichael's family and friends.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
